        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+2 greater resilient greater electricity-resistant chain mail* is adorned with two golden thunderbolts, one along each forearm. Even on a seemingly cloudless day, you can raise your arms to the heavens and draw down a bolt of lightning upon yourself, empowering your armor and blasting your enemies.",
